title: The Everyday Meat Guide (2016) (Pdf) Gooner
description:
The Everyday Meat Guide - A Neighborhood Butchers Advice Book (2016) (Pdf) Gooner

Publisher: Chronicle Books; 01 edition (12 April 2016)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1452142882
ISBN-13: 978-1452142883

The only super-simple handbook to buying meat, by a veteran neighborhood butcher (ex-director of meat department at NYCs Fairway Markets) and Rachael Ray's on-show expert. Explains the grades, quality, best values, cuts, and basic ways to cook poultry, pork, lamb, veal, and beefall the essential stuff people ask the person working the meat counter (if there is one) at markets everywhere every day
